text: - My name is Eileen Turner

and I'm the Director of Product
marketing for AWS Security.
I've been with AWS for 14 months.

The most surprising thing
for me in joining AWS
has been the pace of innovation.

And the scale of innovation has
just been incredible to see.
Every day AWS launches something.

As product marketing,
we're a part of that.

I'm really proud of the
work my team has done.

I have never worked with
more talented people.

The caliber of the thoughtfulness,
the raising the bar

of everything we do, the
leadership principles
are really lived here.
Things like taking a bias for action,

knowing when to think big,
knowing when to dive deep,
seeing that lived on a day-to-day
has been incredibly impressive

and really empowers the
team to do their best work.

And for me personally, I've
done the best work of my career
since joining here at AWS.

I've been astounded at
how much I've learned.

I've grown in my career
and and how I think about
my day-to-day and focus on the customer.
(pleasant upbeat music)
